      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The caching mode determines when the image representations use offscreen caches. Offscreen caches speed up rendering time but do so by using extra memory. In the default caching mode ("
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImageCacheDefault"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "), each image representation chooses the caching technique that produces the fastest drawing times. For example, in the default mode, the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSPDFImageRep"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSEPSImageRep"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " classes use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImageCacheAlways"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " mode but the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSBitmapImageRep"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class uses the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImageCacheBySize"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " mode.  For a list of possible values, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsimagecachemode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". This value is set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSImageCacheDefault"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " by default. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For more information on image caching behavior, see the "
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "title": "Images",
              "destination": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/Cocoa/Conceptual/CocoaDrawingGuide/Images/Images.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40003290-CH208"
            },
